:0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T04:45:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n早兩日都睇番啲香港保衛戰既資料<br />\n好想再知多啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以前係學校根本就唔會學到</blockquote><br />\n可以睇孤獨前哨<br />\n同 重光之路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5be3b25c935368a470988f70ba0f7a4dc2b9ad95","tid":28303,"uid":42550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T04:47:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我記得香港保衛戰，英軍烈士中，有1隻 拉布拉多。 有無人有多d資料。<br />\n<br />\n話隻狗，英軍養，有場游擊戰，衝去戰場咬走左個手留彈後自爆，救左一隊小隊。 烈士當中，計埋呢隻神犬。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n搵到<br />\n神犬達根，最後被追封中士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n義犬報恩        根達中士<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://kwantailo.files.wordpress.com/2013/01/sgt-gander.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkwantailo.files.wordpress.com%2F2013%2F01%2Fsgt-gander.jpg&h=a8e5aa54&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n與奧斯本差不多時間，根達(Gander)中士同樣犧牲了。根達並非人類，而是一頭紐芬蘭犬。牠體型龐大，不少人以為牠是一頭熊。根達原名叫Pal，曾經抓傷小孩面部，差點要人道毀滅。後來軍人Fred收養牠，改名為Gander，自此成為加拿大皇家來福槍團的吉祥物。後來，根達賜為中士，得以隨團來港。日軍在筲箕灣鯉魚門一帶附近登岸，牠會狂吠及去咬日軍；當日軍進逼受傷的加拿大軍，牠曾偷襲日軍，逼使日軍改變路線，救了不少受傷士兵；後來根達看到日軍投擲手榴彈，眼看受傷士兵避無可避，牠一口把手榴彈帶到遠處，最後爆炸而亡。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁勁隻狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7f3eb91051ec1bf224c28dbcd77421f58229b8d","tid":28303,"uid":59298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T05:01:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>當年既香港守軍雖然係雜牌軍<br />\n但仲頂得耐過新加坡d英軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無計啦 對住山下奉文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2aaecce40485464abd9f1f05d424fedb97574c12","tid":28303,"uid":59298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T05:03:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>當年既香港守軍雖然係雜牌軍<br />\n<br />\n但仲頂得耐過新加坡d英軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n加拿大軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我為左紀念依班烈士<br />\n<br />\n去買左個加拿大出既香港保衛戰75週年銀仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/g6dy8bjz\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fg6dy8bjz&h=53c44351&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我11月如果着外套都會戴poppy pin<br />\n<br />\n每日特登做果22下掌上壓</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Bdn61jM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBdn61jM.jpg&h=c67b3c05&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/08/112933_b9d3bf4877dc365c074dd4bb1127a91d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F08%2F112933_b9d3bf4877dc365c074dd4bb1127a91d.jpg&h=b7fca562&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n早排行完黃泥涌，見到pillbox旁的樹有poppy pin紀念佢地</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n行城門碉堡仲有d街名<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n要守住攝政街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc3ac85d931bcb5b8015efa83d2e2056d20f587e","tid":28303,"uid":18555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s