7bcBtqGN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=2d8b9129\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=1460075294022533</a><br />\n<br />\n加拿大政府post悼念香港保衛戰75週年"},{"pid":"002b18e5ea17d5ca373c62c64250fee9c32f517a","tid":28303,"uid":32713,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T05:13:11.000Z","msg":"英國政府都刻意淡化呢段歷史就真既"},{"pid":"6fcf40d67acfd9e32597117d36456e787cc2ba40","tid":28303,"uid":34410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T05:47:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>英國政府都刻意淡化呢段歷史就真既</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n當年英國政府水鳩加拿大話香港好安全 希望佢地派D軍隊黎駐守下，盡下盟國義務 等英國可以集中兵力應付歐洲戰場<br />\n<br />\n結果加拿兵一到 香港保衛戰就開打<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f8c80f3c1df77eef52b75fe25c7071f4d2537f8","tid":28303,"uid":49247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T05:48:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f6cd9c9fdcb64efe1def5582c492ffdab17299c","tid":28303,"uid":34511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T05:50:08.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"ea74639f8b6d81ac6adec8fbd9e87438fcde3cd8","tid":28303,"uid":53284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T06:16:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>英國政府都刻意淡化呢段歷史就真既</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n當年英國政府水鳩加拿大話香港好安全 希望佢地派D軍隊黎駐守下，盡下盟國義務 等英國可以集中兵力應付歐洲戰場<br />\n<br />\n結果加拿兵一到 香港保衛戰就開打<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n9up la"},{"pid":"0a1c19878b7573cfdff83a6565ffe0fc4767129d","tid":28303,"uid":18736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T06:17:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>當年既香港守軍雖然係雜牌軍<br />\n<br />\n但仲頂得耐過新加坡d英軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n加拿大軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我為左紀念依班烈士<br />\n<br />\n去買左個加拿大出既香港保衛戰75週年銀仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/g6dy8bjz\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fg6dy8bjz&h=53c44351&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我11月如果着外套都會戴poppy pin<br />\n<br />\n每日特登做果22下掌上壓</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Bdn61jM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBdn61jM.jpg&h=c67b3c05&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/08/112933_b9d3bf4877dc365c074dd4bb1127a91d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F08%2F112933_b9d3bf4877dc365c074dd4bb1127a91d.jpg&h=b7fca562&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n早排行完黃泥涌，見到pillbox旁的樹有poppy pin紀念佢地</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n行城門碉堡仲有d街名<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n要守住攝政街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u0s413A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu0s413A.jpg&h=82d63827&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0Q8P349.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0Q8P349.jpg&h=2a7463f5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jQ8PR40.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjQ8PR40.jpg&h=fe220696&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之前都有行城門碉堡"},{"pid":"b57cf2989f495aa59a8e57ccc663fb6af775b3ba","tid":28303,"uid":60189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T06:45:43.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"e4996fe8cfd0a3f6ca32edc9293c3954edfa8a01","tid":28303,"uid":21225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T07:57:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7d62e6385f1c8009d6c67f81f60f132316ddfab","tid":28303,"uid":54344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T08:28:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f352a9b5a239d53d2023fd26dca580ac4a17c904","tid":28303,"uid":6372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T08:30:00.000Z","msg":"Respect<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"248ea4a931f4ae8ccbd4c5559bae01715e7c74fd","tid":28303,"uid":54344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T08:33:50.000Z","msg":"班士兵為左一個彈丸之地咁犧牲，宜家個政府就因為政治原因選擇埋沒呢段歷史<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 分分十年二十年後已經冇人記得呢班加拿大人(仲有其他英軍)為香港，為自由付出過佢地嘅生命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c51a1112e8448139fe29b2f446302f37683f53f6","tid":28303,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T08:36:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我記得香港保衛戰，英軍烈士中，有1隻 拉布拉多。 有無人有多d資料。<br />\n<br />\n話隻狗，英軍養，有場游擊戰，衝去戰場咬走左個手留彈後自爆，救左一隊小隊。 烈士當中，計埋呢隻神犬。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n搵到<br />\n神犬達根，最後被追封中士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n義犬報恩        根達中士<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://kwantailo.files.wordpress.com/2013/01/sgt-gander.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkwantailo.files.wordpress.com%2F2013%2F01%2Fsgt-gander.jpg&h=a8e5aa54&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n與奧斯本差不多時間，根達(Gander)中士同樣犧牲了。根達並非人類，而是一頭紐芬蘭犬。牠體型龐大，不少人以為牠是一頭熊。根達原名叫Pal，曾經抓傷小孩面部，差點要人道毀滅。後來軍人Fred收養牠，改名為Gander，自此成為加拿大皇家來福槍團的吉祥物。後來，根達賜為中士，得以隨團來港。日軍在筲箕灣鯉魚門一帶附近登岸，牠會狂吠及去咬日軍；當日軍進逼受傷的加拿大軍，牠曾偷襲日軍，逼使日軍改變路線，救了不少受傷士兵；後來根達看到日軍投擲手榴彈，眼看受傷士兵避無可避，牠一口把手榴彈帶到遠處，最後爆炸而亡。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁勁隻狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有立碑比佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5da1d5bc54b90a17c609ec8fe598f32c3b2c4cde","tid":28303,"uid":498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T09:29:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>當年既香港守軍雖然係雜牌軍<br />\n但仲頂得耐過新加坡d英軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無計啦 對住山下奉文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n香港英軍都對住粟林忠道參謀長...呢條友係硫磺島打到美軍傷亡慘重<br />\n<br />\n好似新加坡果邊得澳洲兵係比較守得住....印度兵真係食屎"},{"pid":"48e8971a9ca29659cf5adeac98e6bf103f2f9b02","tid":28303,"uid":498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T09:30:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>英國政府都刻意淡化呢段歷史就真既</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n當年英國政府水鳩加拿大話香港好安全 希望佢地派D軍隊黎駐守下，盡下盟國義務 等英國可以集中兵力應付歐洲戰場<br />\n<br />\n結果加拿兵一到 香港保衛戰就開打<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n9up la</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n加拿大兵d重裝備好似去到菲律賓比美國佬扣左黎用...隻貨船慢過運兵隻客輪"},{"pid":"97482c5e8ccb53116dcf1986608cfa62e7e1667a","tid":28303,"uid":2649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T09:39:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5cd9bc445eadae6e797ac3d6fe6742dad4b4f16","tid":28303,"uid":59626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T09:40:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11221350e46ea452933ccfabd3bdec3f7e7ee0bd","tid":28303,"uid":53284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T10:18:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>英國政府都刻意淡化呢段歷史就真既</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n當年英國政府水鳩加拿大話香港好安全 希望佢地派D軍隊黎駐守下，盡下盟國義務 等英國可以集中兵力應付歐洲戰場<br />\n<br />\n結果加拿兵一到 香港保衛戰就開打<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n9up la</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n加拿大兵d重裝備好似去到菲律賓比美國佬扣左黎用...隻貨船慢過運兵隻客輪</blockquote><br />\n唔係扣，係未運得切來啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n加軍十一月十六號先到香港，未夠一個月，日軍已經開戰"},{"pid":"7b69f8c31ea98071329ed49a56932f9c1a6ff5fc","tid":28303,"uid":53284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T10:23:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>當年既香港守軍雖然係雜牌軍<br />\n但仲頂得耐過新加坡d英軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無計啦 對住山下奉文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n香港英軍都對住粟林忠道參謀長...呢條友係硫磺島打到美軍傷亡慘重<br />\n<br />\n好似新加坡果邊得澳洲兵係比較守得住....印度兵真係食屎</blockquote><br />\n相反，香港戰役果兩個印度營都表現唔錯"},{"pid":"e5f9ecfa9c73787a50edba7c5103627009a5542f","tid":28303,"uid":53284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T10:24:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>英國政府都刻意淡化呢段歷史就真既</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n當年英國政府水鳩加拿大話香港好安全 希望佢地派D軍隊黎駐守下，盡下盟國義務 等英國可以集中兵力應付歐洲戰場<br />\n<br />\n結果加拿兵一到 香港保衛戰就開打<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n9up la</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n加拿大兵d重裝備好似去到菲律賓比美國佬扣左黎用...隻貨船慢過運兵隻客輪</blockquote><br />\n因為啲裝備十二月十二日先去到菲律賓，果時香港已經畀日本海軍封鎖左，運唔到去香港。"},{"pid":"613ec0971a6571e18159d02d58cb6fd4d9159037","tid":28303,"uid":38192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T10:25:31.000Z","msg":"留名"}]}